      "id": "PopularPost300730",
      "post_content": "\"One Ring to rule them all,  \nOne Ring to find them,  \nOne Ring to bring them all  \nand in the darkness bind them.\"  \n  \nJ.R.R. Tokien said it best. This ring is definitely a monster. Paying ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol) mana to produce ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol). You basically rampant growth on Turn 1, yes that just happened. If you have 2 Sol Rings in your opening hand, the game has just become out of reach for your opponent, just have a 5 mana lead to their 1 mana. Its basically like a quadruple stone rain. I don't know how anyone can give this less than a 4.5, simply amazing card. ",
      "posted_by": "vantha",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost300730\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">\"One Ring to rule them all,<br/>One Ring to find them,<br/>One Ring to bring them all<br/>and in the darkness bind them.\"<br/><br/>J.R.R. Tokien said it best. This ring is definitely a monster. Paying <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/> mana to produce <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/>. You basically rampant growth on Turn 1, yes that just happened. If you have 2 Sol Rings in your opening hand, the game has just become out of reach for your opponent, just have a 5 mana lead to their 1 mana. Its basically like a quadruple stone rain. I don't know how anyone can give this less than a 4.5, simply amazing card. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '300730'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy73424\">vantha</span>\r\n                                (2/19/2013 9:05:21 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"s